{"messageId": "14bb03601662e78a", "headers": {"From": "Curtis M. Faith <curtis.m.faith@gmail.com>", "Date": "Sat, 21 Feb 2015 23:35:00 -0800", "Subject": "[opencog-dev] Suggestions for Dockerfile Additions"}, "body": "Any objections to adding gdb and python-dbg to the Dockerfile? It sure comes in handy having a debugger and Python debugging symbols."},
{"messageId": "14bc0e62f2e2e95c", "headers": {"From": "Amen Belayneh <amenbelayneh@gmail.com>", "Date": "Wed, 25 Feb 2015 05:21:22 -0800", "Subject": "[opencog-dev] Re: Suggestions for Dockerfile Additions"}, "body": "As part of a pull request in the docker repo your suggestions have been added."},
