{"messageId": "14be0e77b56f1aa8", "headers": {"From": "Curtis Faith <curtis.m.faith@gmail.com>", "Date": "Tue, 3 Mar 2015 13:30:38 -0500", "Subject": "Re: [opencog-dev] Re: Suggestions for Dockerfile Additions"}, "body": "I noticed you were using a different directory in the docker repository. We should probably consolidate these Dockerfiles."},
